    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#39;ve never been to one to bake with anything other than all purpose flour, simply because I&#39;m always worried that if I buy whole wheat flour or buckwheat flour or, in this case, dark rye flour, that I will not use all of it and it will just go rancid in my pantry&#8230; but you make this recipe sound good enough for me to take the risk and just try it.<br />And, as always, your pictures look lovely.</p>
    </div>

