    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Thanks Molly for highlighting these: I bake from Good to the Grain all the time and seriously had never noticed them (maybe it&#39;s the recipe header about them requiring lots of components that switches on the blank part of my brain). And compartmentalising the stages seems like a great way to prepare for baking with a baby on the hip, when I imagine all things get done in short snatches&#8230; Good luck with the writing!</p>
    </div>

