      <p>Love Kim Boyce&#39;s book. I made these bars last night and devoured a quarter of the batch before I could stop myself! They are dangerous! I was in such a hurry to try them that I skipped the 30 min freeze time and didn&#39;t grind up the oats (partly b/c I like big chewy oaty bits) and they still turned out amazing. Also a great way to use up all the random jars of jam that are lying about my pantry.</p>
