    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Dear Molly,</p>
<p>I found your blog a while ago and I have been an addict to it since then. I never wrote a comment before, but I have made so many of your recipes. I love your stories and your photos so much.</p>
<p>You have been a true inspiration and now I have my own food blog, which is only a month old.</p>
<p>I hope you can take a look at it.<br /><a href="http://www.spoonglish.com" rel="nofollow ugc">http://www.spoonglish.com</a></p>
<p>Thank you so much! And congratulations for the baby!</p>
<p>Maria</p>
